    <summary>CLI for TokenMix — one API key for GPT-5, Claude, Gemini, DeepSeek and 155+ LLMs</summary>
    <description><![CDATA[
TokenMix CLI gives you command-line access to GPT-5, Claude, Gemini, DeepSeek and 155+ other LLMs through a single OpenAI-compatible API.

## Install

    choco install tokenmix-cli

This package depends on Rust (rust-ms) and uses `cargo install tokenmix-cli` to fetch the latest version from [crates.io](https://crates.io/crates/tokenmix-cli).

## Quick Start

Get a free API key at [tokenmix.ai](https://tokenmix.ai) ($1 free credit, no credit card).

    $env:TOKENMIX_API_KEY = "tm-your_key_here"
    tokenmix chat "Hello"
    tokenmix models

## Other Languages

- Python: `pip install tokenmix-tg-bot`
- Node.js: `npm install -g tokenmix-tg-bot`
- Rust: `cargo install tokenmix-cli`
- .NET: `dotnet add package TokenMix.AI`
- Ruby: `gem install tokenmix`
- PHP: `composer require tokenmixai/tokenmix-php`
- Go: `go get github.com/TokenMixAi/tg-ai-bot/go`
- Docker: `docker pull tokenmixai/tg-ai-bot`

[Get a free API key](https://tokenmix.ai)
]]></description>
